Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:36.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,STARDUST 游戏结果已满是漏洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:41.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,DEAD OR LIE DEAD OR LIE 希冀能看到自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:46.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,GO OUT 在这憋闷的夜晚 我终将被腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:51.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无形的武器已然到手 LIAR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:56.92,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了什么 要守护什么 才经过漫长等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这颗子弹破坏一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:06.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER LIE 即使在这仅剩黑白 暗无光辉的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:11.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,NEVER END NEVER LIE 心灵绝不沾染黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:17.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,THE END OF WORLD 在绝望中握住仅存的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:26.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,用颤抖的手指瞄准目标 去追寻未来！
Comment: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDJP——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終わりが始まるアリアと共に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:02.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白旗を掲げた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:08.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脱獄の果てに歓声の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手錠突き付けられ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:18.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ほら、見て　愚かな駒よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断罪の茶番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}独壇場Funky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その目で見ろ　競争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}Forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.88,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多発的な展開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人の波を掻き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫べ　My Justice，Right Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Make it a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感心できるのはFunky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喪失だけが拒止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}導いてよ　Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鮮烈過ぎた年回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偏見のあるカテゴライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.15,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Don't believe no story
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I know you're ready
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No, we're already over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.07,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Everybody loves despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I'll sadly go from the end
Comment: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,——————————————EDCN——————————————
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴随着结尾即开始的咏叹调
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:02.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高举白旗的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:08.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃狱后的欢呼声中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被强行拷上了手铐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:18.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这定罪的把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:34.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:34.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多线并行的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:39.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拨开人群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:42.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊着 这是我正义的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}许下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得赞美的惊恐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯独拒绝丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:55.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:57.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过于艳丽的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:22:59.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.15,0:23:04.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都爱着绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:11.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会满怀悲伤地离去
